A section on Uses of Diatoms is very essential in view of the decline in fish stock and catch, eutrophication of water, ocean acidification, algal blooms, fish kills, dead zones, etc.
/* Uses of Diatoms */ This is section is very essential, vital to human well being due to need to increase fish production and solve water pollution problems.
/* Phytoplankton decline */ Decline in diatoms in Lake Michigan and Baltic and the causes thereof are discussed.
